  "texts": [
    "ConclusionIn our study, female students had less computer knowledge and previous coding education than male students, although they placed digital literacy equally important.",
    "The students from Nursing scored lowest in the digital literacy questionnaire after those from the Nutrition and Dietetics department.",
    "The highest scores were obtained by Biomedical Engineering students, followed by the students from the School of Medicine.",
    "Participants scored the highest in \"network\" and \"A.I. \"",
    "and lowest in \"interest-knowledge\" domains."
  ],
